<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM1.6.4">
<l>vampulāṅ kūntaṉ maṉaiviyait tuṟantu</l>
<l>piṟarpporuḷ tārameṉ ṟivaṟṟai</l>
<l>nampiṉā riṟantāl namaṉṟamar paṟṟi</l>
<l>yeṟṟivait teriyeḻu kiṉṟa</l>
<l>cempiṉā liyaṉṟa pāvaiyai pāvī</l>
<l>taḻuveṉa moḻivatark kañci</l>
<l>nampaṉē vantuṉ tiruvaṭi yaṭaintēṉ</l>
<l>naimicā raṇiyat tuḷentāy.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Forsaking [our] wives with tresses where fragrances waft,</l>
<l rend="indent">those [of us] who desired these: the wealth and wives of others,</l>
<l>If [we] die, fearing the taunting, “Sinner! Embrace [this] maiden</l>
<l rend="indent">made of copper which has risen from the fire!”</l>
<l>As the minions of Death speak, grabbing, stabbing, [and] capturing [us],</l>
<l>Lord, coming [here], I took refuge at your divine feet,</l>
<l rend="indent">my father in Naimiśāraṇyam.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
